<html>

<head>
	<title>Plastrack Sustainability Tips</title>
	<meta charset = "utf-8">
	<meta name = "viewport" content = "width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<link href = "css/bootstrap.min.css" rel = "stylesheet">
	<link href = "css/bootstrap-theme.min.css" rel = "stylesheet">
	<link href = "css/tips.css" rel = "stylesheet">
	<link href = "css/navbar.css" rel = "stylesheet">
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Reem+Kufi&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manjari&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Josefin+Sans:wght@100;200;300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lexend+Deca&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Righteous&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
    	h2{font-family: 'Lexend Deca', sans-serif;
    font-size: 40px;};
    	body {font-family: 'Manjari', sans-serif; font-size:16px;}
    </style>
</head>

<body>
		<div class="col-xs-12" id=space>
			<div class="jumbotron navigation-bar">
				<div class="dropdown">
					<img id = side-button src="assets/hamburger.png" style="max-width:100%; max-height:100%;"></img>
					<div class="dropdown-content">
				{{#each navLink}}
				<a class="links-hidden" href="{{url}}"><p class="dropdown-font"><p>{{title}}</p></a>
				{{/each}}
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="iconbtn">
					{{#each navIcon}}
					<div class="home-btn">
						<button class="settings">
							<a href="{{url}}" title="{{link-title}}"><img src="{{src}}" style="max-width:100%; max-height: 100%;"></img></a>
						</button>
					</div>
					{{/each}}
				</div>
			</div>		
		</div>

	<div class="container">
		<div class ="row">
			<div class = "col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 title">
						<div class="container"></div>
					<h2 class = "plastrack" style="color:#DFD32B ;text-shadow: 2px 1px 1px #333;">{{moduleTitle}}</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col1">
				<div class="jumbotron tip-titles" id = title style="font-family: 'Lexend Deca', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; color:white;background-color:#314882; border: 2px solid #223971; box-shadow: 3px 2px 1px #15203B; text-shadow: 2px 1px 1px #15203B; text-align:center; border-radius: 0px;">
					Why reduce our plastic waste? 
				</div>
				<div class="well2 descriptions" >
					Sometimes, it can feel pointless trying to reduce our plastic waste usage; since all of these plastic products have already been manufactured, won't someone else end up using them if we don't?
					While feelings like those are valid to a degree, and indicate that systemic change is important, the start of said systemic change comes with indivduals showing less reliance on plastic products. 
					
				</div>
	
	
				{{#each tips}}
				<div class="section">
				<div class="jumbotron tip-titles" id = title>
					{{title}} &raquo;
				</div>
				<div class="well descriptions" id = desc>
					{{desc}}
				</div></div>
				{{/each}}
	
					<div class ="row">
			<div class = "col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 title">
					<h2 class = "plastrack" style="color:#314882;text-shadow: 2px 1px 1px #d1d1d1;">{{moduleTitle2}}</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
				<div class="jumbotron tip-titles" id = title style="font-family: 'Lexend Deca', sans-serif; background-color:#314882; color:white; text-align:center; border-radius: 0px; text-shadow: 2px 1px 1px #15203B; border: 2px solid #223971; box-shadow: 3px 2px 1px #15203B;">
					{{plastrackTitle}} :
				</div>
				<div class="well2 descriptions">
					{{plastrackDesc}}
	
				</div>
			{{#each info}}
			<div class="section">
				<div class="jumbotron tip-titles" id = title>
					{{title}} &raquo;
				</div>
				<div class="well descriptions" id = desc>
					{{desc}}
				</div></div>
				{{/each}}
	
			</div>	
		</div>
	</div>
	

	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
	<script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
	<script src="js/tips.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
